Topic description:
- Book: Szeliski, R. (2022). Computer vision (2nd ed.). doi:10.1007/978-3-030-34372-9
- Chapter 2: Image formation
- Topic 2.1: Geometric primitives and transformations
- Subtopic 2.1.1: 2D Transformations

Post content:
- Basic 2D planar transformations:
	- Translation
		- #DoF: 2
		- Preserves: Orientation
	- Rigid (Euclidean)
		- #DoF: 3
		- Preserves: Lengths
	- Similarity
		- #DoF: 4
		- Preserves: Angles
	- Affine
		- #DoF: 6
		- Preserves: Parallelism
	- Projective
		- #DoF: 8
		- Preserves: Straight lines
	
